<li id="cite_note-click-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-click_3-0" title="">^</a></b> Hanson, Brian. <a href="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/the-click/2007-06-09" class="external text" title="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/the-click/2007-06-09" rel="nofollow">The Click: June 9–15</a>. Anime News Network. Retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-08-16"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-16"><a href="/wiki/August_16" title="August 16">August 16</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-abc2-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-abc2_4-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.abc.net.au/tv/guide/abc2/200707/programs/ZY9080A001D3072007T210000.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.abc.net.au/tv/guide/abc2/200707/programs/ZY9080A001D3072007T210000.htm" rel="nofollow">ABC2 TV Guide: 03 July, 2007</a>. Retrieved <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-10-23"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="10-23"><a href="/wiki/October_23" title="October 23">October 23</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Fun-Gen-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Fun-Gen_5-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="press release" id="CITEREF.5B.5BAnime_News_Network.5D.5D2008"><a href="/wiki/Anime_News_Network" title="Anime News Network">Anime News Network</a> (2008-07-03). <i><a href="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-07-03/funimation-entertainment-and-geneon-entertainment-sign-exclusive-distribution-agreement-for-north-america" class="external text" title="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-07-03/funimation-entertainment-and-geneon-entertainment-sign-exclusive-distribution-agreement-for-north-america" rel="nofollow">FUNimation Entertainment and Geneon Entertainment Sign Exclusive Distribution Agreement for North America</a></i>. <a href="/wiki/News_release" title="News release">Press release</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-07-03/funimation-entertainment-and-geneon-entertainment-sign-exclusive-distribution-agreement-for-north-america" class="external free" title="http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-07-03/funimation-entertainment-and-geneon-entertainment-sign-exclusive-distribution-agreement-for-north-america" rel="nofollow">http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-07-03/funimation-entertainment-and-geneon-entertainment-sign-exclusive-distribution-agreement-for-north-america</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-22</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=FUNimation+Entertainment+and+Geneon+Entertainment+Sign+Exclusive+Distribution+Agreement+for+North+America&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BAnime+News+Network%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BAnime+News+Network%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2008-07-03&amp;rft.series=%5B%5BNews+release%7CPress+release%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animenewsnetwork.com%2Fpress-release%2F2008-07-03%2Ffunimatio